  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile: a SHA-256 content hash is present but no digital signature is included, leaving structural integrity unverifiable (W-SI-01). Full 13-factor assessment is provided. Decision: Accepted.",
