      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must have documented version control, regression testing, and release validation records consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver has version control and unit tests documented, but formal regression test suite coverage falls short of the level required for MRL 5. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
    },
    {
